au.com.cybersearch2.classynode

Class NodeEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.com.cybersearch2.classynode.NodeEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Node

    @Entity(name="nodes")
public class NodeEntity
extends Object
implements Serializable
    NodeEntity Persistent anchor for a component of a graph. Each node has a model which identifies what the node contains and is mapped by ordinal to an enumeration constant. The top node of a graph has a special model called "root". Graph parent and child relationships are expressed as OneToOne and OneToMany respectively.
    Author:
    Andrew Bowley 05/09/2014
